    <div xml:id="PN357">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>kuṉṟutalai maṇanta malaipiṇit tiyāttamaṇ</l>
<l>potumai cuṭṭiya mūva rulakamum</l>
<l>potumai yiṉṟi yāṇṭici ṉōrkku</l>
<l>māṇṭa vaṉṟē yāṇṭuka ṭuṇaiyē</l>
<l>vaitta taṉṟē veṟukkai vi<gap quantity="9" reason="lost" unit="character"/></l>
<l><gap quantity="49" reason="lost" unit="character"/>ṇai</l>
<l>puṇaikai viṭṭōrk karitē tuṇaiyaḻat</l>
<l>tokkuyir vauvuṅ kālai</l>
<l>yikkarai niṉṟivarn tukkarai koḷalē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Over the earth fettered [and] tied with mountains that join [their] heads as hills,</l>
<l>over the world of the Three that was pointed out as common,</l>
<l>over those who ruled without [it] being common</l>
<l>the years rule, don’t they? Help,</l>
<l>there is none available. Riches……..</l>
<l>………………………………….</l>
<l>Difficult for those who let go of the raft, at the time [their] lives</l>
<l>are snatched [away] while [their] companions cry,</l>
<l>is, after having stood on this shore, climbing [and] reaching that shore.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
